Race.SpecificTitle: Marsh Bayou Gravity Drainage District -- 10 Mills Renewal - BOC - 10 Yrs.
Race.SummaryText:
Marsh Bayou Gravity Drainage District Proposition
(Millage Renewal)
Race.FullText: Shall Marsh Bayou Gravity Drainage District of the Parish of Jefferson Davis, State of Louisiana (the "District"), continue to levy a special tax of ten (10) mills on all the property subject to taxation within the District (an estimated $16,700 reasonably expected at this time to be collected from the levy of the tax for an entire year), for a period of ten (10) years, beginning with the year 2021 and ending with the year 2030, for the purpose of the maintenance, construction and improvement of drainage works within and for the District, including the acquisition of equipment therefor?
